# Optional in local dev (Vite proxies /api to port 8000).
# Required for production builds (Vercel, etc.): set in the host’s env at build time.
# Must be your FastAPI base URL — not your Vercel frontend URL.
# Example: https://job-tracker-9uq8.onrender.com  (origin only — do not append /api/... or /docs)
# VITE_API_URL=
